If you look at *ApplicationTemplates files there was a "replacement" pattern like
this.process = null /* $Processes$ */; -> this.process = new Processes(this);
Now that all the models are injectable this is no more needed except for the scenario with annotator == null (no Quarkus/Spring) so I decided to make this explicit and skip the replacement in this case

